üîë API Key: your-openai-api-key-here
üõ°Ô∏è Enable safety checks? [Y/n]: Y

‚úÖ Configuration saved successfully!
```

#### `config reset` - Reset Configuration

**Format:**

```bash
vibeprompt config reset
```

**Example:**

```bash
